{
  "texts": [
    "To investigate the general applicability of comparative assessment, we cover a range of standard NLG evaluation tasks and datasets as follows:",
    ") is a summary evaluation benchmark of 100 passages, each with 16 machine-generated summaries.",
    "Each summary is evaluated for coherency (COH), consistency (CON), fluency (FLU), and relevancy (REL).",
    "Podcast (Manakul and Gales, 2022) is for benchmarking podcast summary assessment methods.",
    "It contains 179 podcasts each with 15 abstractive summaries."
  ]
}